rust-proxmox-sendmail (1.0.1-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * encode non-ascii filenames to improve compatibility.

  * move filename in content disposition headers for attachments to a
    dedicated line to better accommodate longer filenames.

  * allow specifying the masked (noreply) receiver.

  * base64 encode: more efficient line-wrapping implementation.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Sun, 12 Oct 2025 16:18:45 +0200

